Package: SoilUnitAnalysis
Title: NRCS Soil Unit and NEON AOP Analysis for the Santa Rita Experimental Range
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Moore", , "davidjpmoore@arizona.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Combines NRCS soil units with NEON AOP remote sensing products
    to describe spatial patterns in plant species distribution and traits
    on the Santa Rita Experimental Range. Not a distributable package — this
    DESCRIPTION exists so that renv, roxygen2, and testthat tooling work.
